						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Viruppaṇṇa. Śaka 1316 = A.D. 1397.</hi></p>						

						<p>(Śaka 1316 (wrong), <hi rend="italic">Īshvara, śu., ēkādasi</hi>, Thursday and <hi rend="italic">Rēvathi</hi> = A.D. 1397, March 29, Thursday.).</p>						

						<p>Built in at the bottom and incomplete. Seems to refer to a grant (?) of Nāraṇavēḷāṉ to the temple of Tiruppulippagava Nāyaṉār in Pattūr, a hamlet of Madhurāntaka-chaturvēdimaṅgalam in Kaḷattūrk-kōṭṭam of Jayaṅkoṇḍachōḻa-maṇḍalam.</p>						

						<p>Published in <hi rend="italic">KANMK.</hi>, Nos. 39/2005, p. 133.</p>						

